    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on Atrea’s journey, a princess who gets her mind swapped with a minotaur! A puzzle fighter RPG where your choices shape your fate. Duel your friends in multiplayer mode. Talk or fight your way through +100 levels to reclaim your throne in a combination of turn-based and real-time gameplay.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/8db458e31db1e0e6bf24289dcddb8d75.avif?t=1737671452\" width=605 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/da527840a4a60d3fc6082bca394b5427.poster.avif?t=1737671452\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/da527840a4a60d3fc6082bca394b5427.webm?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/da527840a4a60d3fc6082bca394b5427.mp4?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>Match pieces to perform powerful moves! A better combination could mean the difference between a fireball and a meteor!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/5f61d1abf8980eaa26199719995febcc.avif?t=1737671452\" width=605 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/66b764f3b04b21133e0d4e6a0ebd9e09.poster.avif?t=1737671452\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/66b764f3b04b21133e0d4e6a0ebd9e09.webm?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/66b764f3b04b21133e0d4e6a0ebd9e09.mp4?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>Challenge your friends! Play as popular characters from the campaign in multiplayer mode!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/47803e00a1ebf2f219156919ddeaa36e.avif?t=1737671452\" width=605 height=101 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/06adabff893c8abdb6be03cf2f540dbd.poster.avif?t=1737671452\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/06adabff893c8abdb6be03cf2f540dbd.webm?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/06adabff893c8abdb6be03cf2f540dbd.mp4?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Overcome challenges in the 7 realms, throughout 100+ levels! Explore the beautiful world of Akrotheria.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/f4e07f465674dc00f80ba0a3a631a2f3.avif?t=1737671452\" width=605 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/75021e429aa1743e88187c7d4ba29799.poster.avif?t=1737671452\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/75021e429aa1743e88187c7d4ba29799.webm?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/75021e429aa1743e88187c7d4ba29799.mp4?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Pick your abilities and level up an intricate skill tree! These powers may change the tide of battle.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/0501aacef81366f89cb5e59c639fbfe8.avif?t=1737671452\" width=605 height=101 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/fe6974f757631780d42f6e755e60a796.poster.avif?t=1737671452\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/fe6974f757631780d42f6e755e60a796.webm?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885400/extras/fe6974f757631780d42f6e755e60a796.mp4?t=1737671452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>Your choices matter! Be a brute or be polite, you decide which of the 100+ characters will be your enemies or allies.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
